data.description: Golden Opportunity, come see all that Country living has to offer. Shy three acres of land with a huge 40X60 shop with 600 amps, 480 volts, and 3 phase power and a three stall barn. Horses, cattle, sheep, will all flourish here. The home features four bedrooms, 2 1/2 Baths and a large deck for entertaining, or just overseeing your domain. Cook out and entertain with your fully equipped outdoor kitchen. Relax in the Hot Tub while you soak away your stress and pains. It also has a Lighted basketball court. There is lots of room for Gardens so you can grow your own vegetables. You'll appreciate the Electric Gate at the driveway. This way you won't be getting un-expected visitors.  Down Payment Assistance Up to $42,037 (5% of Total Loan Amount)
